- aws proprietary MySQL and PostgreSQL compatible relational database

- aurora provides the speed, performance and scale of popular commercial databases
  with the simplicity of the more common open source databases

- provides fault-tolerant and self-healing storage system which lowers the risk of data loss

AURORA SCALING

- uses cluster volumes

- storage auto scaling

- self healing storage

- cache warming

- spreads data across 3 az using data copies

- 2 copies of data is stored 3 azs 

- 100% cpu utilization
   - issue with WRITES: scale up the instance size
   - issue with READS:increase read replicas

- aurora serverless is the auto scaling version of aurora
